## 1. DEFINITIONS

**"Software"** refers to LocalDBKit, including all source code, documentation,
and associated files.

**"You"** refers to the individual or legal entity exercising permissions
under this License.

**"Personal Use"** means use by an individual for non-commercial purposes.

**"Small Business"** means an organization that meets one of the following:
  a) Has fewer than 10 total employees (full-time equivalent), OR
  b) Has total annual gross revenue less than ¥100,000,000 JPY
     (approximately US $1,000,000)

**"Commercial Use"** means any use primarily intended for commercial advantage
or monetary compensation.

**"Modified Version"** means any derivative work or modification of the Software.

**"Change Date"** means 2029-03-16.

